Information

Rich Kids Go Shopping
Documentary exploring the lives of five 18 to 21-year-olds, and their desire to make and spend money. The youngsters sharing their secrets to success include 19-year-old Dhillan Bhardwaj, who owns a booming urban fashion business that started in his garage and has become a multi-million-pound retail empire. Cameras also follow Jamie Pine, 20, and his 19-year-old boyfriend Mike. They have amassed millions of viewers for their lucrative online vlogs, which they film and produce in their Plymouth home.
